com.github.robocup_atan.atan.parser

Interface CommandFilter


  • public interface CommandFilter
    An interface that shall help to filter the different server commands (see, hear, error, ...). Implementations of this interface are used as parameter for the parser which will call the Appropriate methods. As probably not all messages from the server will have to be completely parsed the command filter acts as a preselection of commands.
    Author:
    Atan
